On Sun, 3 Jan 1999, Anders Semb Hermansen wrote:
Anders: This latest message of yours appeared 3 times on the list.
If you pull out the NIC does your drive work OK?
My drives ran slow on 2.0.36 until I disabled all nis in
nsswitch.conf, only keeping dns. It made a world of difference. 
Weird but it worked. I got the tip from this list.
If all fails stick with 2.0.36 and be patient  
Lykke til!
